Simple node.js comet -> websocket bridge 

Intended initially for use with RestMQ, can be used for any COMET endpoint or can be adapted to use long polling. 

Also can send back data received via ws.

Depends on: http://github.com/gimite/web-socket-js (bundled)

gleicon - 2011 - http://www.7co.cc | http://github.com/gleicon

